<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>GitHub Trending: Fortran, Today</title><link>https://github.com/trending/fortran?since=daily</link><description>The top repositories on GitHub for fortran, measured daily</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2019 00:05:35 GMT</pubDate><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2019 00:05:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>PyRSS2Gen-1.1.0</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><ttl>1400</ttl><item><title>modern-fortran/tcp-client-server #1 in Fortran, Today</title><link>https://github.com/modern-fortran/tcp-client-server</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;A minimal Fortran TCP client and server&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="instapaper_body md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-tcp-client-server" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#tcp-client-server"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;tcp-client-server&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A minimal TCP client and server in Fortran, used to teach interoperability with C.
Companion code for Chapter 11 of &lt;a href="https://www.manning.com/books/modern-fortran?a_aid=modernfortran&amp;amp;a_bid=2dc4d442" rel="nofollow"&gt;Modern Fortran: Building Efficient Parallel Applications&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It uses &lt;a href="http://libdill.org" rel="nofollow"&gt;libdill&lt;/a&gt; as a sockets library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-getting-started" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#getting-started"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Getting started&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download and build the code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;git clone https://github.com/modern-fortran/tcp-client-server
cd tcp-client-server
make
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-running-the-server" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#running-the-server"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Running the server&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In one terminal window, run the server:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;./server 
 Listening on socket:
   IP address: 127.0.0.1                                    
   Port:         5555
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-running-the-client" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#running-the-client"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Running the client&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In another terminal window, run the client:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;./client 
                    5 Hello 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On client connection, the server will report:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt; New connection from 127.0.0.1
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><author>modern-fortran</author><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.com/modern-fortran/tcp-client-server</guid><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>